$TRSH ART GALLERY POPUP:

SPONSORED BY ROBNESS CYBERPOP IN COLLABORATION WITH POWERSURGE(@SERGEUIV) PROVIDING THE PLOT.

-------
WHAT LIES BEFORE YOU IS A COLLECTION OF WORK THAT SPANS A YEAR, DURING THE CORONAVIRUS PANDEMIC OF 2020.  ONE WOULD CALL IT THE YEAR WHERE CRYPTO ART WAS IN FULL BLOOM, WHEN THE PHYSICAL ART WORLD DISAPPEARED AND THUS WAS REPLACED BY A NEW RENAISSANCE THAT SHOWED A FLOWERING OF DIGITAL ART BEING RAREIFIED BY UTILIZING BLOCKCHAIN TECHNOLOGY. THE WORK YOU SEE BEFORE YOU HAS BEEN INSPIRED BY THE ORIGINAL ART PIECE THAT WAS BANNED BY SUPERRARE.CO ENTITLED '64 GALLON TOTER.'  THE ONGOING ART DEBATE ABOUT 'WHAT IS ART?' STILL EXISTS TO THIS DAY AND THIS GALLERY COULD NOT HAVE EXISTED WERE IT NOT FOR ARTISTS AROUND THE GLOBE CONTRIBUTING THEIR FEELINGS AND EXPRESSIONS TO THAT SUBJECT.  

THIS PLOT IS ALSO A HOME BASE FOR THE $TRSH CONCEPTUAL ART PIECE, A CRYPTO ART MARKET BOOTSTRAPPED TO ROBNESS' CRYPTO ART CAREER.

Support $TRSH    
The first ever conceptual art piece on Uniswap.  
Art Shards (tokens) available on Uniswap exchange.
